 158:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) DirectionChangeCallback           : TIM Direction Change Callback
 159:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) IndexErrorCallback                : TIM Index Error Callback.
 160:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) TransitionErrorCallback           : TIM Transition Error Callback
 161:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c **** 
 162:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****   [..]
 163:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c **** By default, after the Init and when the state is HAL_TIM_STATE_RESET
 164:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c **** all interrupt callbacks are set to the corresponding weak functions:
 165:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****   examples HAL_TIM_TriggerCallback(), HAL_TIM_ErrorCallback().
 166:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c **** 
 167:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****   [..]
 168:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****   Exception done for MspInit and MspDeInit functions that are reset to the legacy weak
